rows.label: tlk70000063_05_msg0001
rows.name:
Why can Blades make use of ether
like they do?

rows.label: tlk70000063_05_msg0002
rows.name:
And why does the ether produced by
Divine Beasts create miasmas?

rows.label: tlk70000063_05_msg0003
rows.name:
I'm drowning in a sea of questions
with few answers to cling to...

rows.label: tlk70000063_05_msg0004
rows.name:
Hm... But what if Blades and Divine Beasts
weren't differing species at all...?
That would change everything...

rows.label: tlk70000063_05_msg0005
rows.name:
Listen to me! I've gotten way ahead
of myself. That can't be the case.

rows.label: tlk70000063_05_msg0006
rows.name:
It's just too many leaps of logic.
Maybe all this research is making me a
bit hare-brained... Ahahahaha!
